title: BSIDE U0 Open Jaw Digital Multimeter Tester Fully Automatic with Smart Clamp Meter AC DC Current 1-100A Pocket Mini Non Contact Voltage Detector Rechargeable for Electricians Beginners
features: [Totally Smart]: This fully automatic multimeter is designed for quick circuit checks for electricians or beginners, easy to use, all functions in the device is auto. It can recognize automatically AC DC voltage/current, resistance, continuity, and live wire etc.
[Open Jaw Meter]: True RMS clamp meter with fixed fork, handy for quick checks. It measures both AC and DC current 1-100A automatically and contactlessly. Manual mode is availlable as well.
[Voltage Detector]: Can be a non-contact voltage tester pen, detecting the presence of voltage (12V-1000V/90V-1000V) with adjustable high/low setting, buzzer and visual alarm on large screen.
[Pocket Size]: Compact and refined shape, easy to carry or slip into your pocket, this mini clamp meter is especially suitable for testing in tight spaces such as hubs or dense wiring.

[Rechargeable and More]: With a built-in rechargeable battery and a brilliant flashlight, long hours of work and wiring in dark are no longer a problem. And this voltmeter ammeter features a large screen with big, stable and accurate readings, allowing you to better assess real-time conditions and risks when working around electricity.
description: Features: Pocket mini tester meter rechargeable AC DC Clamp meter, smart multimeter and voltage detector 3 in 1 Non contact AC DC current measurement Automatic Test of AC DC voltage/current, continuity, and resistance Zero function for accurate DC current testing NCV Tester with buzzer alarm and double sensitivity Non contact/in contact live wire search Super large colour LCD with: Test value with large digits Auto switch-off function Low battery indication Anti burned and anti overcharge protection Built in LED flashlight for wiring in dark Specifications: Display: 4000 counts DC Voltage: 0.800-3.99V/39.99V/399.9V/610V, 0.001V/0.01V/0.1V/1V, (0.8%+3) AC Voltage: 0.800-3.99V/39.99V/399.9V/610V, 0.001V/0.01V/0.1V/1V, (1.0%+3) DC Current: 1-100.0A, 0.1A, (2.5%+5) AC Current: 1-100.0A (40-1000Hz), 0.1A, (2.5%+5) Resistance: 5Ω-40MΩ, 1Ω, (1.2%+3) Continuity: Buzzer beeps when measured resistance is less than 50Ω NCV: Up to 1000V AC voltage with adjustable sensitivity Live Wire Search: Yes Auto power off: 15 minutes Power: 3.7V battery rechargeable Size: 192 x 36 x 30 mm Weight: 101g Package Includes: Open Jaw Multi Tester Test Leads Charging Cable User Manual Please note: To get a more accurate test value, please zero the readings before testing DC current due to the role of the Earth's electromagnetic field!
